:{"Dialogue":["","Precious little things, aren't they?"]},"9743":{"Dialogue":["","Raising funds for a good cause *and* increasing clientele..."]},"9744":{"Dialogue":["","Why don't we try the festive meals they're serving at the lounge?"]},"9745":{"Dialogue":["","I'm sure they won't mind you playing with the otters for a bit."]},"9746":{"Dialogue":["","That innocent, otterly gaze... It's irresistible!"]},"9747":{"Dialogue":["","That aside, where is the otter-shaped pudding!? I was promised *pudding*!"]},"9748":{"Dialogue":["","Aren't they just delightful?"]},"9749":{"Dialogue":["","Awww, that's so kind of you to\u2500oh. You meant the otters."]},"9769":{"Dialogue":["","Pip pip!"]},"9770":{"Dialogue":["","Pip. Prrr pip!"]},"9771":{"Dialogue":["","How oddly endearing..."]},"9772":{"Dialogue":["","That tiny little top hat...! Oh, my heart can't take this!"]},"9773":{"Dialogue":["","Such a striking silken suit! Sewed specially for them, surely?"]},"9774":{"Dialogue":["","Didn't expect 'em to prance around on their hind paws..."]},"9775":{"Dialogue":["","We tavernkeeps can never stay away from the food for long, it seems..."]},"9776":{"Dialogue":["","Where'd ye like to go next, ladies?"]},"9847":{"Dialogue":["","That Manderville's a clever one, he is!"]},"9848":{"Dialogue":["","But the cats... The cats..."]},"9858":{"Dialogue":["","...Are you lookin' to ride the rafts?"]},"9859":{"Dialogue":["","..."]},"9860":{"Dialogue":["","Remember, take turns...!"]},"9861":{"Dialogue":["","I get the one in front!"]},"9862":{"Dialogue":["","Let's go ride the mografts!"]},"9863":{"Dialogue":["","Tilt your head right down when you dive, all right?"]},"9864":{"Dialogue":["","Nothing like a good spot of fishing!"]},"9865":{"Dialogue":["","My lord, pray do not overexert yourself in this heat..."]},"9866":{"Dialogue":["","I'll wager you couldn't land a fish if it bit you in the arse! "]},"9867":{"Dialogue":["","I'll try my best!"]},"9868":{"Dialogue":["","Be at ease, for you are under the vigilant eye of the Coastguard!"]},"9869":{"Dialogue":["","Nothing to report."]},"9870":{"Dialogue":["","My paws are itching to dance, kupo!"]},"9871":{"Dialogue":["","If I approach at a sprint, then perhaps..."]},"9872":{"Dialogue":["","Maybe if I try *one* more time...I'll make it over..."]},"9873":{"Dialogue":["","The one who jumps into the smallest target wins!"]},"9874":{"Dialogue":["","I could stay here forever..."]},"9875":{"Dialogue":["","Drinks are on the loser!"]},"9876":{"Dialogue":["","My turn to jump in next."]},"9877":{"Dialogue":["","If I aim for that target...!"]},"9878":{"Dialogue":["","Rats, I thought I had it!"]},"9879":{"Dialogue":["","Okay, so for our next pose..."]},"9880":{"Dialogue":["","How about we...<pant>...take a break?"]},"9881":{"Dialogue":["","Here you go\u2500chilled and refreshing!"]},"9882":{"Dialogue":["","Can I offer you a drink?"]},"9883":{"Dialogue":["","Ah, that hits the spot! Another!"]},"9884":{"Dialogue":["","Well, it would be rude not to..."]},"9919":{"Dialogue":["","The whole world must know this exhilaration! This triumph!"]},"9920":{"Dialogue":["","Phew...my wings ache, kupo."]}}}